overview: Wicked Legends Vol. 2 lives up to its name by putting together some of the hottest performers from the early 2000s to ever appear in Wicked releases! This second volume showcases scenes that feature Devinn Lane, Sydnee Steele, Kylie Ireland, Miko Lee, and many other beautiful girls from a variety of Wicked titles, such as Park Avenue, Lovers Lane, Partners Forever, and Pornomatic 2000 among others. This volume of "Turn of the Century" Wicked scenes is a must-have for any fan of Wicked!
title: Wicked Legends 2
